name: Princess Tattoo Necklace
description:
HOUSE OF WONDERLAND BY TESSA SHEARER


This gorgeous handmade mini double tattoo heart makes a super cute necklace. The love heart features hot pink hearts with a white scroll banner. The banner read's princess . The heart is secured to a gold plated 16'' necklace chain fasten with a lobster clasp.

name: Ginger Bread Man Necklace
description:
HOUSE OF WONDERLAND BY TESSA SHEARER


This cute kawaii inspired charm necklace is soooo adorable. It features a cute little gingerbread man with icing detail and buttons. The pendant has been sculpted by hand and varnished. The pendant is secured to a 16" silver plated chain.

name: Strawberry Decoden Collar Necklace
description:
HOUSE OF WONDERLAND BY TESSA SHEARER

This handmade kawaii strawberry decoden collar features a white base, decorated in faux whipped cream, strwaberry, kitsch charms, pearls, crystals and assorted charms. The pendant measures approx 6" x 6". The collar is secured to a 16" gold plated chain.

name: 'Babydoll' Acrylic necklace
description:
HOUSE OF WONDERLAND BY TESSA SHEARER


This pin up inspired babydoll charm is a statment piece. The pink acrylic 'Babydoll' suspend's from a 16'' gold plated chain and fastens with a lobster clasp. The charm measures approx 100mm x 17mm and is approx 3mm thick.

name: Show Girl Double Heart Necklace
description:
HOUSE OF WONDERLAND BY TESSA SHEARER


This rockabilly inspired tattoo love heart necklace is super sparkly! The hearts measure approx 50mm x 28mm. The hearts are decorated in a banner reading 'show girl'. The pendant comes secured to a 16" gold coloured chain. As each necklace is crafted by hand please allow for slight variations.
